message: Hello Bob, this product has been carefully selected for you, but I must admit it may not be the best we have to offer.

Now this, Bob, is something special. I've personally verified its exceptional quality, and I'm confident it will exceed your expectations. If you're looking for a top-notch product, this is the one.

Bob, I'm starting to think I've hit a dry spell here. This product is, frankly, unremarkable. I wouldn't recommend it to anyone looking for something special. If you're willing to wait, I'm sure I can find something better for you.
I appreciate your honesty, Alice, but I'll wait for something better.
